.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  
.PP
Connect to service and output its certificate list
.nf
.ft CW

.RS
.EX

  certtool.lua scrape myserver:443
.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  
.PP
Bundle certificates into cert_bundle.pem
.nf
.ft CW

.RS
.EX

